Package: A2SIT
Title: Admin2 Severity Index Tool
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("William", "Becker", , "william.becker@bluefoxdata.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6467-4472"))
Description: This package is the container for a shiny app which allows
    non R-users to build their own Severity Index using their own data.
    Aside from containing the shiny app, the back end code is all
    accessible, and can be used for other purposes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/UNHCR-Guatemala/A2SIT
